module TopModule (
    input logic a,
    input logic b,
    input logic c,
    input logic d,
    output logic out
);

    always @(*) begin
        out = (a & ~b & ~c & ~d) | // 00 00
              (a & ~b & d) |     // 00 10
              (a & c & ~d) |     // 01 00
              (b & ~c & d) |     // 10 01
              (b & c) |          // 11 01
              (c & d);           // 11 11
    end

endmodule
